content: I'm glad you provided all these healthy snack options. I usually meal prep on Sundays and bring healthy snacks to work, which has helped me cut down on junk food and stay motivated. I'm thinking of trying some protein-rich snacks like Greek yogurt or hard-boiled eggs to support my weightlifting classes, like BodyPump on Mondays. Do you have any tips on how to keep them fresh and convenient at work?
